{
  "texts": [
    "Data sets in the observations category can be originating from any domain such as health informatics, environmental science, business, commerce, etc.",
    "Data could be collected online or offline from reports or studies.",
    "A wide range of problems can be assessed from the following repositories: the PMLB (Olson et al. 2017), the OpenML (Vanschoren et al. 2013), and the UCI (Dua and Graff 2017).",
    "An exemplary application in this category is wind speed forcasting (Abdellaoui and Mehrkanoon 2021).",
    "Measurements represent sets of data points that are collected (and sometimes analysed) in physics experiments."
  ]
}